            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">Nero Clau</supplied>dius <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>beri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Drusus</supplied> <expan><abbr>Germanic</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetor</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>uaestor</ex></expan> proco<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Nero Cla<supplied reason="lost">udius Caesar</supplied> <lb n="2"/>Drusus Ge<supplied reason="lost">rmanicus</supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>beri</ex></expan> Claudi Ca<supplied reason="lost">esaris</supplied> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> Ger<supplied reason="lost">manici <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Kolumne II, Z. 3: I-longa: 7.5 cm. Zwei aneinanderpassende Teile der Inschrifttafel mit zwei Kolumnen erhalten. Beide Kolumnen sind augenscheinlich vom selben Steinmetzen, aber nicht zeitgleich eingemeißelt worden: Kolumne I: 41/43 n. Chr.; Kolumne II zwischen dem 25. Februar 50 n. Chr. (Aufnahme in die gens Claudia) und dem 13. Oktober 54 n. Chr. (Tod des Claudius).</p>
            </div>
